impact investing&nbsp; where investments are made to companies, organizations and funds with the intention to generate a measurable, beneficial social or environmental impact alongside a financial return.\nThe proceeds are used to invest in a well-selected portfolio of debt and equity securities mostly&nbsp;to microfinance institutions and social enterprises operating in the Philippines; as well al small scale real estate projects. The Company is designed to accommodate small social investors seeking capital appreciation and positive social impact.&nbsp;","type":"control_text"},{"name":"clickTo21","qid":"21","text":"For investors who would like to build and&nbsp;preserve&nbsp;their savings&nbsp;and wants positive social impact\nHigher Returns- compared to time deposit of commercial banks and government treasury bills\nInvested in Strong Institutions in the Philippines- mainly in microfinance institutions and social enterprises\nProfessionally Managed","type":"control_text"},{"name":"clickTo22","qid":"22","text":"Terms and Conditions\n\nMinimum Investment: PhP5,000.00\nInvestment Term: 1 year, minimum\nDocumentation: Preferred Stock Certificate\n\n&nbsp;\n\n\n\nInvestment Amount\nDividend Rate\nNet Return, if pre-terminated\n\n\n&nbsp;PhP 5,000.00 - PhP 49,999.00\n&nbsp;3%\n&nbsp;0%\n\n\n&nbsp;PhP 50,000.00 - PhP 249,999.00\n&nbsp;4%\n&nbsp;1%\n\n\n&nbsp;PhP 250,000.00 - PhP 500,000.00\n&nbsp;5%\n&nbsp;2%\n\n\n&nbsp;&gt; PhP 500,000.00\n&nbsp;3%\n&nbsp;0%\n\n\n","type":"control_text"},{"name":"clickTo23","qid":"23","text":"How to invest ?\n1. Accomplish the online registration form\n2. You will receive an email on how to&nbsp;place your initial&nbsp;investment and how to&nbsp;notify&nbsp;SEDPI about your investment\n3. Deposit the amount to SEDPI's bank account only.\n4. SEDPI will validate your investment and you will be able to view your investment in the online system by viewing your transactions.\n5. You may add to your investment anytime. There is no required frequency as long as you meet the minimum investment amount for each.\n&nbsp;","type":"control_text"},{"name":"clickTo24","qid":"24","text":"Frequently Asked Questions\n\n\n\n1. Can we add investments anytime?\nYes, with a minimum of Php 1,000.00\n\n\n2. Can we withdraw our investments? How?\nYes, you can.&nbsp;Just visit SEDPI Social Investor Online, select I am a SEDPI social investor and use the code emailed to you.&nbsp;\n\n\n3.&nbsp;How long is the withdrawal process?\nUsually two weeks.\n\n\n4.&nbsp;Can I have a beneficiary?\nYou are required to elect at least one beneficiary.\n\n\n5.&nbsp; Is the dividend rate the same every year?\nNo, it depends on the performance of the organization and is set every January.\n\n\n6. Is there a passbook?\nNo. You will receive a stock certificate representing preferred shares.\n\n\n","type":"control_text"},{"name":"divider25","qid":"25","type":"control_divider"},{"name":"beneficiaries","qid":"26","text":"Beneficiaries","type":"control_head"},{"description":"","name":"beneficiary1","qid":"27","text":"Beneficiary 1","type":"control_fullname"},{"description":"","name":"relationship1","qid":"28","subLabel":"e.g. Mother, father, friend etc.","text":"Relationship 1","type":"control_textbox"},{"description":"","name":"beneficiary2","qid":"29","text":"Beneficiary 2","type":"control_fullname"},{"description":"","name":"relationship2","qid":"30","subLabel":"","text":"Relationship 2","type":"control_textbox"},{"description":"","name":"beneficiary3","qid":"31","text":"Beneficiary 3","type":"control_fullname"},{"description":"","name":"relationship3","qid":"32","subLabel":"","text":"Relationship 3","type":"control_textbox"},{"name":"pageBreak33","qid":"33","text":"Page Break","type":"control_pagebreak"},null,{"name":"pageBreak","qid":"35","text":"Page Break","type":"control_pagebreak"},{"name":"adviceInvestment","qid":"36","text":"Advice investment deposit ","type":"control_head"},{"name":"pageBreak37","qid":"37","text":"Page Break","type":