ort.\nAlalay sa Kaunlaran, Inc. (ASKI) is a microfinance NGO that provides financial services to low income groups in Central and Northern Luzon. SEDPI extends loans to ASKI. Interest rate for investors is 9% per annum, fixed. Minimum investment is PhP10,000. Download partner's appraisal report.\nPantukan Chess Club Cooperative (PCCC) is a cooperative that provides financial services to low income groups in Compostella Valley. SEDPI extends loans to PCCC. Interest rate for investors is 8% per annum, fixed. Minimum investment is PhP10,000.\nUnited Sugar Planters Cooperative (USPD) is a cooperative that provides financial services to low income groups in Davao del Sur. SEDPI extends loans to USPD. Interest rate for investors is 9% per annum, fixed. Minimum investment is PhP10,000.\nTagum Coop (TC) is a cooperative that provides financial services to low income groups mostly in Mindanao with headquarters in Davao del Norte. SEDPI places share capital in Tagum Coop. Dividend rate for investors is 7-10% per annum, variable. Minimum investment is PhP10,000.","type":"control_text"},{"name":"theSocial","qid":"157","text":"THE SOCIAL INVESTMENTS LISTED&nbsp;DO NOT CARRY ANY GUARANTEE. YOU BEAR 100% OF THE RISK SHOULD YOU DECIDE TO INVEST.","type":"control_text"},{"name":"theSocial158","qid":"158","text":"In the event that the chosen investment is already oversubscribed, SEDPI will notify the investor and the amount will be&nbsp;credited to SEDPI wallet until further instructions from SEDPI.\nPreferred shares have 3% exit fee when redeemed before two years.&nbsp;Debt assignments have 3% entry fee and 3% exit fee when redeemed before two years.","type":"control_text"},{"name":"clickTo","qid":"159","text":"Initial investment deposit report\nAdditional investment report\nNew members report\nWithrawal request report\nList of social investor application submissions","type":"control_text"},{"name":"pageBreak160","qid":"160","text":"Page Break","type":"control_pagebreak"},{"name":"h