            <h2>

              How to invest ?

            </h2>

            <p style="padding-left: 30px;">1. Accomplish the online registration form</p>

            <p style="padding-left: 30px;">2. You will receive an email on how to place your initial investment and how to notify SEDPI about your investment</p>

            <p style="padding-left: 30px;">3. Deposit the amount to SEDPI's bank account only.</p>

            <p style="padding-left: 30px;">4. SEDPI will validate your investment and you will be able to view your investment in the online system by viewing your transactions.</p>

            <p style="padding-left: 30px;">5. You may add to your investment anytime. There is no required frequency as long as you meet the minimum investment amount for each.</p>

