            <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">THE SOCIAL INVESTMENTS LISTED DO NOT CARRY ANY GUARANTEE. YOU BEAR 100% OF THE RISK SHOULD YOU DECIDE TO INVEST.</span></p>

